{"TopicId":87837,"ForumId":21,"TopicTitle":"Sidereal MK IV Orbital Fighter","CreatedByName":"Ganymede","CreatedById":60469,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-10-19T00:19:18Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Ganymede","CreatedById":60469,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-10-19T00:19:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003EIntroducing the Sidereal, a craft solely built for zero gravity combat.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/bVogI58.png\u0022 alt=\u0022bVogI58.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/uLhEp0u.png\u0022 alt=\u0022uLhEp0u.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003EI really wanted to incorporate the new wing shapes into a fighter design.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/ZW6uEb7.png\u0022 alt=\u0022ZW6uEb7.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003EThe large pylons give plenty of area to attach munitions.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/LJXp93n.png\u0022 alt=\u0022LJXp93n.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003EEdit: I\u0027ve made a companion craft to increase the delta-v needed for long trips.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/W0PK5nO.png\u0022 alt=\u0022W0PK5nO.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAn important note: After you dock the Sidereal to the companion ring, press action group 1. \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThis will toggle the fighter\u0027s reaction wheels and keep it from trying to torque itself off of the docking node.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EYou can download the craft here:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/iwbz4cv8adzck26/Sidereal%20Mk_%20IV.craft?dl=0\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.dropbox.com/s/iwbz4cv8adzck26/Sidereal%20Mk_%20IV.craft?dl=0\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe companion craft can be found here:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/34crzrjm6v6001p/Sidereal%20Mk_IV%20Companion.craft?dl=0\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.dropbox.com/s/34crzrjm6v6001p/Sidereal%20Mk_IV%20Companion.craft?dl=0\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222014-10-19T21:25:13Z\u0022 title=\u002210/19/2014 09:25  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 19, 2014\u003C/time\u003E by Ganymede\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-10-19T08:39:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ELooks interesting.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHow much Delta-v has it got?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ganymede","CreatedById":60469,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-10-19T15:53:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EAlone, the ship has 1,355 m/s. That\u0027s not much to get to places, so I made a companion craft. Together they have 6,126 m/s.\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}